Brooks -

At present, you can&#39;t do much more with them than what you describe.  
This class was initially developed to do multiphase equilibrium, and 
has the methods to support that.  It certainly is useful for other 
things, and the set of methods needs to be enlarged..,

Most of what you want to do is possible with Mixture objects in  C++ 
(although there the class is called &quot;MultiPhase&quot;). All that is lacking 
are the bindings for Python / MATLAB to access the C++ methods.

Dave


